  "topic": "arrays",
  "difficulty": "easy",
  "statementMd": "Given an array of integers `nums` and an integer `target`, determine whether **two distinct positions** `i` and `j` exist such that `nums[i] + nums[j] == target`.\n\nReturn `true` if such a pair exists, otherwise `false`.",
